QC & QA Officer - PT MC PET Film Indonesia
QC & QA Officer  -
QC & QA Officer
Responsibilities
MaleMaximum 26 years oldCandidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Engineering (Chemical) or equivalent.Required language(s): EnglishAt least 1 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Preferably Staff (non-management & non-supervisor)s specializing in Quality Control/Assurance or equivalent.Full-Time position(s) available.Willing to be placed in Cilegon area DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES Maintain routine and non routine inspection and measurement in order to perform jobs smoothly and effectively.Judge measurement result by following Internal Film Specification in order to satisfy customer.Control and maintain quality control equipments, its spare part, chemical and consumable goods to keep the equipment ready for using.Control and manage the quality control equipment maintenance and calibration which is done by operator in order to keep equipment fit and accurate for inspection and measurement based on ISO9001 standard.Control and maintain standard sample in order to keep inspection level.Check and analyze the daily QC data every day and confirm the reliability of the data and inform to superior and MFG Section Officer when it is find some strange QC data.Treat the inspection data using statistical technique to clarify the results.Control and manage Keep Product and Hold Product by checking the problem in order to guarantee product quality.Make report of equipment trouble and support superior in doing investigation on finding the trouble cause.Measure and analyze a film for special items that the superior orders.Make Standard Operation Procedure (SOP), and educate it to QC operators and confirm the education results.Make Certificate of Analysis to certify that the product meets customer requirement by collecting quality data.Make the investment plan in order to develop quality control activities more effective and accurate.Implement of ISO 9001 and ISO 14000 activities.Practice of Corporate Compliance in work life and environmental.Support Supervisor to improve atmosphere and environment of work place by cooperating with related persons in order to create active, bright and disciplined section.
